name: pylyzer

about.summary: A fast static code analyzer & language server for Python
A fast static code analyzer & language server for Python

raw_meta_yaml:
schema_version: 1

context:
  version: 0.0.82

package:
  name: pylyzer
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/mtshiba/pylyzer/archive/v${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c2b30b29764321ba2f2be50cbeded24add03bc17a663a92825b1bce8a60ba24c

build:
  number: 2
  script:
    - cargo-bundle-licenses --format yaml --output THIRDPARTY.yml
    - ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation

requirements:
  build:
    - ${{ compiler('c') }}
    - ${{ stdlib("c") }}
    - ${{ compiler('rust') }}
    - cargo-bundle-licenses
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - python
  host:
    - python
    - maturin >=0.12
    - setuptools-rust
    - pip
  run:
    - python

tests:
  - requirements:
      run:
        - pip
    script:
      - pip check
      - pylyzer -h

about:
  summary: A fast static code analyzer & language server for Python
  license: MIT
  license_file:
    - LICENSE
    - extension/LICENSE
    - THIRDPARTY.yml
  homepage: https://github.com/mtshiba/pylyzer

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - danielnachun
    - thewchan
